---
---
<section id="sobre" class="py-24 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <!-- Image with Montgomery frame -->
    <div class="relative reveal h-full min-h-[400px]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/10 rounded-[3rem] -rotate-3 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-0 duration-700"></div>
      <div class="relative h-full bg-slate-100 rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white group">
        <!-- Placeholder -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-300 gap-4 bg-slate-50/50">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 opacity-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] opacity-30">Dr. Geovani Miranda</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Experience Tag -->
      <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-blue-950 text-white p-6 rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl reveal hover:scale-105 transition-transform" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        <span class="block text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter">+10 Anos</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-black tracking-widest text-blue-300 opacity-80">De Experiência Clínica</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="space-y-10 reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="text-primary font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs">A Excelência em Cada Palavra</div>
        <h2 class="text-blue-950 leading-tight">
          Cuidado especializado <br>
          <span class="text-primary italic font-medium">para transformar vidas</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          A fonoaudiologia vai além do tratamento clínico; é o resgate da autoconfiança e da conexão humana. Com foco em resultados reais e tecnologia de ponta, ofereço um atendimento personalizado que respeita o tempo de cada paciente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Qualifications Grid -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-3 p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z" />
              <path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-blue-950 tracking-tight">Formação Premium</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed italic">Especialista em Fonoaudiologia Clínica com foco em Reabilitação.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3 p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-blue-950 tracking-tight">Abordagem Ágil</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed italic">Resultados visíveis através de protocolos modernos e eficientes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-4">
        <a href="#contato" class="btn-primary">Saiba mais sobre mim</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
